Package: MemorySpan
Type: Package
Title: Measure Digit and Letter Spans
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Zakary A. Draper
Maintainer: Zakary A. Draper <zakary.draper@ubc.ca>
Description: A single function for measuring forward and reverse order digit
    and letter span in the R console. The function presents the user with
    a sequence of letters or numbers and asks the user to return that sequence
    in either forward or reverse order. If the user is successful, they are
    presented with another sequence that is 1 character longer than the
    sequence that was previously displayed.
